Look around you. What do you see? Nothing? Nothing but boring stupid life? Is that all you see? Well, I just have to say something to everyone who thinks that they have boring shit fuck life. Your life is what u make it as simple as i put it. Honesty, you could luv ur life no matter how rich or poor (but i would like to be rich, who wouldn't) but thats not the point. the point is who hasn't thought their life was a lttle boring at times, I know I have. A lot of pople just want to grow up and get their childhood over with so they can do what hey want or they are tired of waititng for that day to come good or bad. I think you should just at least try to tell yourself  that ur gonna live the life u want whhther u feel like the worlds on ur side or not make the world on ur side. If y ou feel like you've had a bad day just tell yourself therte a new day tomorrow and u can make it better the next day or the day after. People say life is short but i hate it when they minimize life to being that way. i think Life isn't short it's just that it people make it seem that way because as you live your  so- called looong booring life you can't actually see all the things that are happening around you until one day it seems so short. I think you should just do the things you wanna do. Whenever you feel like there is no one else, no one that you can talk to, talk to God. I know if your not a believer you  think it sounds crazy but just do it cause it may make you feel better. God is always open to anyone willing to let him in and let me tell you life isn't as dark and scary if you just believe, in something. Growing up to me as i am 16, i feel like I don't know wut the hell is going on, i don't know where my life is going but i just want to get there. It's like you find youself in a fog and only you can guide yourself out. I believe anyone can be anything they want to be in life , you have a choice whether you take the right or wrong path it's your choice. I know the right path isn't always the easy one but im sure it'll pay off in the future. 
Well i have done enough jibber jabbering about life n shit haven't I? lol Well i don't even know wut i wrote or if i went over the same thing and if i spelled anything correct but i do you wut im talkin about.
